{"tid":2415842,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★由Tesla到中概股 揭開「契媽」Catherine Wood 團隊香港足跡","createTime":"2021-02-20T14:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T14:59:15.000Z","uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1723cffa8f4e17abe4eb4b83359252938073bc26","tid":2415842,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PenT8dC5Ufs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPenT8dC5Ufs&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=f637b2a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PenT8dC5Ufs</a><br />\n近年說起Catherine Wood的名字，相信股民人人知曉。現年65歲的Catherine Wood在2013年創辦方舟投資〈ARK Investment Management 〉，雖然創立不足10年，但基金以投資顛覆性創新科技板塊，扑中Tesla股價大升，表現跑贏標普500及納斯達克指數，甚至超越了畢菲特〈Warren Buffett〉管理的波克夏海瑟威，過去5年的平均年回報接近40%，除了被稱「女版畢菲特」，更備受一眾連登仔追捧，視為「連登契媽」。能夠跑贏大市，在於「契媽」獨特的投資方向，去年更開始大手吸納中概股。"},{"pid":"f54d09b42313f36ea7ae8508820cd4df040a4a34","tid":2415842,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"記者朋友你好 我係漢語多功能字庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429e7aa2ffd924e129c795b63faba5fe2cefc09d","tid":2415842,"uid":390975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"正呀喂 有重點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}